hopobject.body: Yes, I love it! protamed.com.br One of the best places for bandage dresses in every colour combination possible is Celeb Boutique - we've picked out a bandeau style below but they have a huge range that are also regularly seen on ladies like Luisa Zissman and Chloe Sims. Or why not treat yourself to an original Leger? If you go to Net-a-Porter's outlet site you can get one at a massively reduced price - worth saving up for if you've got a special night planned.
